      "number": "5",
      "title": "Relations",
      "link": "#Relations",
      "children": [
        {
          "number": "5.1",
          "title": "Udyr",
          "link": "#Udyr",
          "children": [],
          "textContent": "Lee Sin is a friend of Udyr who he met in the Freljord. With his help Lee Sin was able to repel Noxian invaders from his homeland, while Udyr was able to find peace and calmness with the help of the monks."
        },
        {
          "number": "5.2",
          "title": "Disciples",
          "link": "#Disciples",
          "children": [],
          "textContent": "While Lee Sin has relations with all of the Shojin Order Dragon disciples, he has some deeper relations with 2 Ying Yue."
        },
        {
          "number": "5.3",
          "title": "Order of Shadow",
          "link": "#Order_of_Shadow",
          "children": [],
          "textContent": "Lee Sin has fought members of the Order of Shadow, presumably because they defy the sacred balance of Ionia."
        }
      ]
    },
